1a0f0c8c794f8aab2a050b660e86f3cba293fcd4d0ffba9a1a1b8fd88f631d68fe194256495ed584d13e577c577829f0bbe821ffaf11165163b5a78c9d68efe8  verbose-testsuite.patch"
